      <title>中国文远知行推迟美国 IPO 截止日期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/china-s-weride-is-said-to-delay-us-ipo-just-as-deadline-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在中国监管机构的批准到期前几天，文远知行（WeRide Inc.）已推迟了其在美国首次公开募股（IPO）的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/china-s-weride-is-said-to-delay-us-ipo-just-as-deadline-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:16:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国顶级经济学家要求政府遏制对初创企业融资的干预</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/top-china-economist-asks-state-to-curb-sway-in-funding-startups</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位著名的中国经济学家呼吁国有资本退出风险投资，允许私营部门在这个关键行业中发挥更大的作用，该行业正经历多年来投资最疲软的时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/top-china-economist-asks-state-to-curb-sway-in-funding-startups</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 01:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前 FTX 内部人士 Salame 称美国违反了女友调查协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/ex-ftx-executive-salame-says-us-broke-deal-on-girlfriend-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前 FTX 高管 Ryan Salame 已请求美国法官撤销对他的定罪或阻止对其女友的任何起诉，指控检察官违背了如果他达成认罪协议就停止调查其女友的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/ex-ftx-executive-salame-says-us-broke-deal-on-girlfriend-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 22:31:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布朗夫曼将对派拉蒙全球的出价提高至 60 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/bronfman-raises-offer-for-paramount-global-to-6-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，媒体投资者埃德加·布朗夫曼 (Edgar Bronfman Jr.) 将收购 CBS 母公司派拉蒙全球 (Paramount Global) 的报价提高至 60 亿美元，这可能会打乱该公司与独立制片人 Skydance Media 合并的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/bronfman-raises-offer-for-paramount-global-to-6-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 22:03:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 上涨，中国科技股下跌 | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-21/nvidia-gains-and-chinese-tech-stocks-sink-bloomberg-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 分析了为什么英伟达在投资者等待经济数据之际的市场大周中领先基准。此外，沃尔玛以 36 亿美元出售京东股份给电子商务公司带来压力，福特为何放弃全电动 SUV 计划。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-21/nvidia-gains-and-chinese-tech-stocks-sink-bloomberg-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 21:15:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Snowflake 给出的前景未能平息投资者对人工智能的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/snowflake-outlook-fails-to-ease-investor-fears-of-competition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Snowflake Inc. 公布的销售前景未能让投资者相信该公司将在人工智能软件工具市场占据一席之地。该公司股价在盘后交易中下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/snowflake-outlook-fails-to-ease-investor-fears-of-competition</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:32:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zoom 预计新产品的销量将好于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/zoom-projects-better-than-expected-sales-growth-on-new-products</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Zoom Video Communications Inc. 公布的本季度销售预测超出了分析师的预期，这表明其扩展的产品套件正在获得商业客户的青睐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/zoom-projects-better-than-expected-sales-growth-on-new-products</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:31:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
